Nine specimens were collected by hand in the intertidal zone of Punta Colorada ( 41 º 46 ' S
, 65 º 00' W
) (
). The specimens were relaxed with menthol crystals for a few hours, fixed in 4 % seawater formalin for two months, and transferred to 70 % ethanol for long-term storage afterwards.

